data.name: XInteractionContinuation
desc: Specifies a way of how to continue from an com.sun.star.task.XInteractionRequest.
Different sub-interfaces of this interface specify different ways of continuing.

methods.name: select
desc: Select this way of continuing from an com.sun.star.task.XInteractionRequest (given a choice of various instances of com.sun.star.task.XInteractionContinuation).
